SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION HAS RETAINED HIGH TECH ROCHESTER, INC., A RELATED 501(C)(3) ORGANIZATION, TO MANAGE AND OPERATE THE INCUBATOR FACILITY AND PROVIDE BUSINESS SUPPORT SERVICES TO THE CLIENT-TENANTS THROUGH FEBRUARY 2016. AS OF MID-FEBRUARY 2016, THE INCUBATOR CEASED OPERATIONS AND HTR REMAINED RESPONSIBLE ONLY FOR MAINTENANCE OF RBC'S FINANCIAL RECORDS. TOTAL AMOUNT PAID FOR THESE SERVICES DURING THE FISCAL YEAR WAS $0.

THE BOARD DOCUMENTS THE BASIS FOR ITS DECISION IN THE MINUTES OF THE MEETING AT WHICH THE DECISION WAS MADE.
